features: EASY TO USE – UK 2 pin to 3 pin adapter plug for shaver / toothbrush is easy and convenient to use. Just simply plug and use!
STURDY & CONVENIENT - Plug for electric toothbrush has compact design, solid construction, is lightweight and made of high quality materials.
PERFECT FOR TRAVELLING – This razor fused wall outlet can be used as a travel adapter with your 2-pin electric item when you go abroad to countries where they use the same 3-pin socket.
QUALITY ASSURANCE – Approved by all safety standards. Provides protection against short circuit, heat-resistant, over-current and over-voltage. 1A fuse approved make it safe to use home or abroad.

UNIVERSAL COMPATIBILITY – Keple universal two to three prong converter allows you to charge an electrical shavers, toothbrushs or epilator from a normal 3 pin UK sockets devices such as: Braun Oral-B electric toothbrush including Professional Care, SmartSeries, TriZone, Advance Power, Pro Health, Triumph, Plak Control 3D, Vitality Precision Clean, Sensitive Clean, White Clean, Panasonic, Omron, Colgate etc.
